<strong>IN&#45;TEXT CITATION</strong>
<br>
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	The Turning Page Bookshop (2056) indicated that&hellip;
	<br>
	Alternatively: A recent report (The Turning Page Bookshop, 2056) showed that&hellip;
</blockquote>
<br>
When the author is referred to more than once in the same paragraph do not include the date in 
subsequent references, as long as the study cannot be confused with others cited.
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	In a recent report, The Turning Page Bookshop (2056) showed&hellip; The Turning Page Bookshop 
	also reported&hellip;
</blockquote>
